      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine your <strong>shredded red cabbage</strong> in a bowl with your<strong> cider vinegar</strong>, 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 tsp] </span><strong>sugar</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, then give everything a good mix up and set aside until later – this is your <strong>quick-pickled red cabbage</strong></p><p>Remove the skin from your <strong>smoked mackerel fillet[s] </strong>and discard</p><p>Tear the <strong>mackerel</strong> into small, bite-sized pieces directly into the pan with the butter beans and cook for 1-2 min further or until warmed through</p><p>Once done, remove from the heat and set aside</p>",
      "order": 3,
