      "instruction": "<p>While the mackerel is cooking, cut your<strong> lemon[s]</strong> into quarters</p><p>Add the juice of 1/4 of the<strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>lemon quarter[s]</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>to a bowl along with your <strong>tamari soy sauce </strong>and 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> – this is your<strong> tamari dressing</strong></p>",
